# MTSA pilot WAR (Trustgate): must be committed so GitHub Actions can docker-build
# apps/signing-gateway/mtsa-pilot. We ignore arbitrary *.war drops locally but force-track
# the one filename CI expects. (Historically WARs were gitignored mainly because they are
# large proprietary vendor binaries—not because our app secrets live in git; avoid committing
# scratch WARs or alternate filenames by keeping the broad *.war rule.)
# mtsa-pilot/webapps/*.war
# !mtsa-pilot/webapps/MTSAPilot.war
